ldTrump (banned 2021; uses Truth Social @realDonaldTrump)", "prev_election_opponent": null, "next_election_year": null, "next_election_contenders": [], "next_election_date": "2028-11-07", "next_election_type": "general", "seat_up_next": false}, "footnotes": {"src-13207d6d": {"url": "https://ballotpedia.org/Donald_J._Trump", "archive_url": null, "title": "Ballotpedia", "publisher": "Ballotpedia", "accessed": "2026-04-24", "excerpt": ""}}, "answer_footnotes": {"america_first": [["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], [], ["src-13207d6d"]], "life": [[], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"]], "immigration": [[], [], [], [], []], "marriage": [[], [], [], [], []], "self_defense": [["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"], ["src-13207d6d"]], "education": [[], [], [], [], []], "christian_heritage": [[], [], [], [], []]}}, {"name": "JD Vance", "slug": "jd-vance", "office": "", "jurisdiction": "Executive Branch", "level": "executive", "party": "R", "district": null, "state": "US", "id": 7592, "scores": {"america_first": [true, true, true, null, null], "marriage": [true, true, true, null, false], "life": [true, false, false, true, true], "self_defense": [true, true, true, true, true], "immigration": [true, true, null, null, true], "education": [true, true, true, true, true], "christian_heritage": [true, true, null, false, null]}, "notes": "Vance scores highest on self-defense (perfect 10) and education (perfect 10). His Catholic conversion through influence of Peter Thiel and study of Augustine shapes his worldview. His 'ordo amoris' argument for prioritizing nationals is distinctly Catholic. Weakest on PCH/CBG due to Catholic universalism vs narrow Anglo-Saxon framing. His 2022 reversal from federal abortion ban to states-rights cost him points.", "photo": "assets/photos/us/jd-vance.jpg", "website": null, "sources": ["https://ballotpedia.org/JD_Vance", "https://www.whitehouse.gov"], "profile": {"rel